name: Ferredoxin : nadp reductase (NFN)

name: Glutamate-5-semialdehyde dehydrogenase

name: C. therm biomass objective function for cellobiose grown cultures  (2% DCW corresponds to cellulase)

name: Branched chain C13 fatty acid synthesis

name: Aldehyde dehydrogenase (acetaldehyde, NADP)

name: Dihydrofolate:NADP+ oxidoreductase One carbon pool by folate / Folate biosynthesis EC:1.5.1.3

name: Glutamate synthase (NADPH)

name: hydrogen-sulfide:NADP+ oxidoreductase
